00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,000
Nona Yao hanya terlalu takut.

272
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,920
Tubuhnya baik-baik saja.

273
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:39,760
Dia akan segera bangun.

274
00:20:40,599 --> 00:20:41,079
Kembalilah.

