00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,119
Baik.

276
00:20:42,599 --> 00:20:43,479
Saya pamit.

277
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,990
Tidak ada satu penjelasan pun?

278
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:15,900
Kau pergi begitu saja?

